libber (0.3.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added functions to encode/decode Trap, GetBulkRequest,
    InformRequest, and SNMPv2_Trap tags.
  * Now uses abz_*_error() functions to report errors.
  * Added regression tests for makeoid().
  * New Makefile system.
  * Created man pages for all the functions on the library.
  * Changed package description.

